wikipedia_page.main: Harley Kemp (born 9 July 1994) is an Australian former professional darts player. He won the Australian Masters in 2013 and qualified for the 2014 BDO World Darts Championship.

response: He qualified for the 2014 BDO World Darts Championship, he played Harley Kemp of Australia in the Preliminary round winning 3–0. He played Ross Montgomery in the First round losing 2–3.2014 BDO World Championship Results. Darts Database
